title: Lifetime-Dear Secret Santa [2013]
description:
Lifetime-Dear Secret Santa (2013) 

Air Date: 30 Nov 2013

Summary: Beverly Hills banker/workaholic JENNIFER comes home to her small Northern California town just before Christmas when her dad, TED , takes a bad fall while putting up decorations. While home, Jenny begins getting romantic Christmas cards from an unknown admirer, who turns out to be her old neighbor and the unrealized love of her life, JACK. There's just one problem- Jack died in a car accident three years ago.
